youknow\")]),s._v(\" \"),n(\"p\",[s._v(\"链接：https://juejin.im/post/5cd9037ee51d456e5c5babca\")]),s._v(\" \"),n(\"p\",[s._v(\"来源：掘金\")]),s._v(\" \"),n(\"p\",[s._v(\"著作权归作者所有。商业转载请联系作者获得授权，非商业转载请注明出处。\")]),s._v(\" \"),n(\"h2\",{attrs:{id:\"_7-localstorage，sessionstorage和cookie的区别\"}},[n(\"a\",{staticClass:\"header-anchor\",attrs:{href:\"#_7-localstorage，sessionstorage和cookie的区别\",\"aria-hidden\":\"true\"}},[s._v(\"#\")]),s._v(\" 7.localStorage，sessionStorage和cookie的区别\")]),s._v(\" \"),n(\"p\",[n(\"strong\",[s._v(\"共同点\")]),s._v(\"：都是保存在浏览器端、且同源的\")]),s._v(\" \"),n(\"div\",{staticClass:\"tip custom-block\"},[n(\"p\",{staticClass:\"custom-block-title\"},[s._v(\"数据存储方面\")]),s._v(\" \"),n(\"ul\",[n(\"li\",[n(\"strong\",[s._v(\"cookie数据\")]),s._v(\"始终在同源的http请求中携带（即使不需要），即cookie在浏览器和服务器间来回传递。cookie数据还有路径（path）的概念，可以限制cookie只属于某个路径下\")]),s._v(\" \"),n(\"li\",[n(\"strong\",[s._v(\"sessionStorage和localStorage\")]),s._v(\"不会自动把数据发送给服务器，仅在\"),n(\"strong\",[s._v(\"本地保存\")]),s._v(\"。\")])])]),s._v(\" \"),n(\"div\",{staticClass:\"tip custom-block\"},[n(\"p\",{staticClass:\"custom-block-title\"},[s._v(\"存储数据大小\")]),s._v(\" \"),n(\"ul\",[n(\"li\",[s._v(\"存储大小限制也不同，\"),n(\"strong\",[s._v(\"cookie数据\")]),s._v(\"不能超过4K，同时因为每次http请求都会携带cookie、所以cookie只适合保存很小的数据，如会话标识。\")]),s._v(\" \"),n(\"li\",[n(\"strong\",[s._v(\"sessionStorage和localStorage\")]),s._v(\"虽然也有存储大小的限制，但比cookie大得多，可以达到5M或更大\")])])]),s._v(\" \"),n(\"div\",{staticClass:\"tip custom-block\"},[n(\"p\",{staticClass:\"custom-block-title\"},[s._v(\"数据存储有效期\")]),s._v(\" \"),n(\"ul\",[n(\"li\",[n(\"strong\",[s._v(\"sessionStorage\")]),s._v(\"：仅在当前浏览器窗口关闭之前有效；\")]),s._v(\" \"),n(\"li\",[n(\"strong\",[s._v(\"localStorage\")]),s._v(\"：始终有效，窗口或浏览器关闭也一直保存，本地存储，因此用作持久数据；\")]),s._v(\" \"),n(\"li\",[n(\"strong\",[s._v(\"cookie\")]),s._v(\"：只在设置的cookie过期时间之前有效，即使窗口关闭或浏览器关闭\")])])]),s._v(\" \"),n(\"div\",{staticClass:\"tip custom-block\"},[n(\"p\",{staticClass:\"custom-block-title\"},[s._v(\"作用域不同\")]),s._v(\" \"),n(\"ul\",[n(\"li\",[n(\"str